          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>LG has expanded its UltraGear lineup with three premium GX9 OLED smart monitors. These all share the same high-end specs--including a vibrant 3440 x 1440 resolution, 0.03ms response time, a 240Hz refresh rate, and come bundled with webOS, which can<strong> access all your favorite streaming platforms</strong>. That should make them a versatile entertainment hub, as they are well-equipped for both high-end gaming and a relaxing movie night. There are <a href="https://www.amazon.com/LG-34GX90SA-W-Ultragear-Compatible-DisplayHDR/dp/B0F15CGTGW?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">34-inch</a>, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/LG-39GX90SA-W-Ultragear-Compatible-DisplayHDR/dp/B0F15C7JL2?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">39-inch</a>, and <a href="https://howl.link/srs70g9xgwdcg?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17437922004949?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">45-inch models</a>, and each are available now.</p><div title="6530638 - LG UltraGear Smart Gaming Monitors" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="3340" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6530638 - LG UltraGear Smart Gaming Monitors" data-collection="">             <h2>                    <a href="https://howl.link/srs70g9xgwdcg?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17437922004949?u1=subid_value" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/howl.link\/srs70g9xgwdcg?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/17437922004949?u1=subid_value\n&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://howl.link/srs70g9xgwdcg?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17437922004949?u1=subid_value ">LG UltraGear Smart Gaming Monitors</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://howl.link/srs70g9xgwdcg?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17437922004949?u1=subid_value" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/howl.link\/srs70g9xgwdcg?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/17437922004949?u1=subid_value\n&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://howl.link/srs70g9xgwdcg?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17437922004949?u1=subid_value ">Starting at $1,400</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>This smart OLED monitor is available in three sizes--45 inches, 39 inches, and 34 inches. Thankfully, you won't be sacrificing any features if you opt for a smaller display, as all three get you the exact same specs. Along with the 3440 x 1440 resolution and 240Hz refresh rate, the display boasts an 800R curve that should result in a better viewing experience. You'll also get an excellent 0.03ms response time that's great for gaming.</p><ul><li><strong>UltraGear 45-Inch OLED Curved Monitor (45GX90SA) -- $1,700</strong><ul><li><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=LG+Launches+Three+New+Premium+Curved+Gaming+Monitors+With+240Hz+Refresh+Rates&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-04-04+11%3A38%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-04-04+16%3A29%3A39&amp;fnarticle_id=6530638&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.lg.com%2Fus%2Fmonitors%2Flg-45gx90sa-b-gaming-monitor&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Flg-launches-three-new-premium-curved-gaming-monitors-with-240hz-refresh-rates%2F1100-6530638%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">See at LG Store</a></li><li><a href="https://howl.link/srs70g9xgwdcg?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17437922004949?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">See at Best Buy</a></li></ul></li><li><strong>UltraGear 39-Inch OLED Curved Monitor (39GX90SA) -- 1,600</strong><ul><li><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=LG+Launches+Three+New+Premium+Curved+Gaming+Monitors+With+240Hz+Refresh+Rates&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-04-04+11%3A38%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-04-04+16%3A29%3A39&amp;fnarticle_id=6530638&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.lg.com%2Fus%2Fmonitors%2Flg-39gx90sa-w-gaming-monitor&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Flg-launches-three-new-premium-curved-gaming-monitors-with-240hz-refresh-rates%2F1100-6530638%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">See at LG Store</a></li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/LG-39GX90SA-W-Ultragear-Compatible-DisplayHDR/dp/B0F15C7JL2?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">See at Amazon</a></li><li><a href="https://howl.link/bkuofwfz9n6sa?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17437924996502?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">See at Best Buy</a></li></ul></li><li><strong>UltraGear 34-Inch OLED Curved Monitor (34GX90SA) -- $1,400</strong><ul><li><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=LG+Launches+Three+New+Premium+Curved+Gaming+Monitors+With+240Hz+Refresh+Rates&amp;fnauthor=brendanhesse&amp;fndate=2025-04-04+11%3A38%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-04-04+16%3A29%3A39&amp;fnarticle_id=6530638&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.lg.com%2Fus%2Fmonitors%2Flg-34gx90sa-w-gaming-monitor&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Flg-launches-three-new-premium-curved-gaming-monitors-with-240hz-refresh-rates%2F1100-6530638%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">See at LG Store</a></li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/LG-34GX90SA-W-Ultragear-Compatible-DisplayHDR/dp/B0F15CGTGW?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">See at Amazon</a></li></ul></li></ul></div>                      </div><p>Other notable features include support for Nvidia G-Sync and AMD FreeSync Premium, and each runs on webOS 24, which lets you access a variety of streaming services, 350 free channels on the LG Channels app, and cloud gaming platforms like GeForce Now and Amazon Luna. The monitors also feature a sleek "virtually borderless design" that maximizes screen space, and can be moved via tilt, height, and swivel adjustment points. They also include hexagonal RGB backlighting for extra flair.</p><p>While these newly released smart monitors look impressive, they're also quite expensive. If you want something more affordable, here's a look at some other great gaming monitors currently on sale. In fact, two LG UltraGear models are on sale right now--including a compact <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DF786923?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">27-inch OLED monitor</a> and an affordable <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0B928B6BC?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">34-inch curved monitor</a>.</p><h2>Best Gaming Monitor Deals</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Monitor-FreeSync-Premium-Refresh-Display/dp/B0C5RW3DPS?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Acer 27-Inch Gaming Monitor</a> -- $200 (<del>$295</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BP94J8VD?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Alienware 34-Inch OLED Curved Monitor</a> -- $782 (<del>$900</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DD2ZB3DZ?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">INNOCN 49-Inch OLED Curved Monitor</a> -- $800 (<del>$1,000</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DF786923?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">LG 27-Inch UltraGear OLED Monitor</a> -- $600 (<del>$900</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0B928B6BC?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">LG 34-Inch UltraGear Curved Monitor</a> -- $260 (<del>$400</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CDQMQQS2?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Samsung 49-Inch Odyssey OLED Curved Monitor</a> -- $950 (<del>$1,600</del>)</li></ul><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/astro-bot-ps5-console-bundle-deals-still-available-at-amazon/1100-6529417/"